Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,프랑크 푸르트\N하나 어떠세요~?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,2학년 2반은\N귀신의 집 하고 있습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,이야~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,첫날부터\N엄청 성황이구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,우리 학교랑은\N완전 딴판이다!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,있지,\N어디부터 돌아볼래~?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,음, 그러니까~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,2반에서 한다는\N귀신의 집 가보고 싶어!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮겠다~!\N가자, 가자!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,오오...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,이쿠요 같은 게\N우글우글댄다
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,일단은~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩네 반이 가까워 보이는데\N보러 가자구!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,오!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.67,0:00:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,여긴가 본데~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,야호~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩, 있어~?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치,\N접대 좀 해봐라
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,선배...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,키타쨩도 메이드복 봇치쨩\N보러 온 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,어디 있음?\N메이드복 봇치쨩, 은
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,그게...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,에에에!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}봇치쨩이 사라졌어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,메이드복을 입히니까
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"화장실 갈래"라면서\N그후로 감감무소식이라...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇게 싫었으면\N미리 말해주지...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,메이드복 입고\N교내를 도망쳐 다니는 게
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,400)}더 창피한 거\N같기도 한데...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,아무튼 찾으러 가자!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,네!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,에에에...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,거기!\N귀찮아하지 말고!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:22.39,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn태 나무\fs50\bord5\c&H090909&\3c&HBEBEBE&\frx348\fry2\frz349.5\pos(1300,485)}이 너머는
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:22.39,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn태 나무\fs50\bord5\c&H090909&\3c&HBEBEBE&\frz343\frx350\fry0\pos(1835,580)}출입금지
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩\N안 보이네~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,어딜 가버린 걸까?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,일단 여자 화장실을\N닥치는 대로 뒤져볼까...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,에엑!?\N전부...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,아뇨...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:02:01.68,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna몬스터\fs30\bord3\shad4\c&H237CE1&\4c&H313475&\3c&H282760&\pos(385,230)}왔다
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:02:01.68,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna몬스터\fs65\bord3\shad4\pos(295,275)\c&H237CE1&\4c&H313475&\3c&H282760&}다윈이 키타!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:02:01.68,Above - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna하얀구름\b0\fs45\bord3\blur3\pos(1800,215)\3c&H2B2B2B&}신발견! 고토 히토리 극비의\N생태계에 다가서다
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨는 그렇게 시종일관\N사람이 있는 곳에는 안 간다구요!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.19,0:01:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,흠~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼\N어디를 찾아야 할까?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,가르쳐줘, 키타 박사님!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,해설에\N들어가볼까 해...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,우선!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,사람이 없고~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,눅눅해서~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,민달팽이가 숨을만한\N장소를 찾는 겁니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,돌밑 같은 곳에\N들러붙어 있답니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\fna두리둥실\fs65\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy200)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\pos(1185,545)\c&HD9ADFF&\3c&H6737C1&}응냨!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,자연스럽게\N혐성 발언을 하네...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}무지성으로 거짓말 하고\N도망쳐버리고 말았다...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}모두한테 민폐일 테니\N돌아가야 하는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그래도\N이런 차림!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}밴드 멤버들한테 보이는 건\N너무 부끄럽잖아...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이럴 때에\N완숙 망고가 있다면~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:25.79,Centor - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs65\bord4\pos(1085,760)}아, 어서 오세요~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그 골판지 상자의\N따스함이 그립다아~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}안 되겠다...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이대로 가다간 멘탈이\N완전히 맛탱이 가버릴 거야...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}현실도피하자~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}인터넷 세계로\N도망가자?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}요즘 밴드 연습 때문에\N바빠서
