Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어라...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}영상 마지막으로 올린 게\N언제였더라...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아, 요즘 매일 바빠서\N올릴 여유가~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}문화제 끝나면\N바로 뭐라도 올리자!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,보세요
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,있잖아요, 고토 씨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,오오~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,반 애들이\N걱정하더라~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 앗, 그...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,진짜 민달팽이가\N있을만한 데에 있었네
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,쓰레기통이나 탱크 속을\N뒤져본 보람이 있었죠!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,사람 찾고 있다는 기분이\N전혀 안 들었지만 말야...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,자, 얼른 돌아가자?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,예...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,오!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,이거 좀 봐~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,봐, 여기!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.88,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna말괄량이\b1\fs90\bord0\c&H373640&\fscx95\fscy95\t(00,3170,\fscx100\fscy100)\move(980,680,980,675,00,3170)}결속밴드
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,우리 이름이 실려 있어!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,근데...\N뭐, 당연한가~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,아하하...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,학교 안에서 결속밴드라는\N이름을 보는 게
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,이상한 느낌이\N드네요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,지금부터 긴장하다간\N쓸데없이 지칠걸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,그러게요!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘은 순수하게\N문화제를 즐겨봐요!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,그치, 고토 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,억...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,으으...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}키타 씨랑은 다르게...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이런 학교 행사가 즐거웠던\N기억이 한 번도 없는데...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,2학년 2반\N귀신의 집~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,줄끝은 여기입니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:06:01.09,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn양재백두체b\b0\fs80\bord6\blur4\pos(850,125)\c&H4A4A4A&\3c&HEDECEC&}2반 유령병동
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,한 분 들어가십니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,사실은 여기가\N좀 궁금해서 말야~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,잠깐 들렀다 가고 싶다\N했거든!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,저도 가고 싶어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,평판 좋다던데요?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,엑...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.32,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fn태 나무\fs70\bord4\pos(1010,290)\c&H8BC5DE&\3c&H465F89&}크레이프
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,다른 데\N또 들러도 돼~?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,초코 크레이프\N나왔습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,초코 바나나...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,아니, 짭짤한 쪽도\N괜찮으려나~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,그냥 둘 다 사!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,나도 한 입 주고
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,물론이죠!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,이보셔~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,자연스럽게\N삥뜯지 마라~
