Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,꽤 오래된 거 같긴 한데...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,아버지랑 가족들도\N내일 오시는 거지?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,저번에는 태풍 때문에\N라이브에 못 와서
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,의욕이\N넘치고 있어요...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,막 비디오 카메라까지\N사기도 하고...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,아하하!\N엄청 상상된다~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.60,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(220,535)}바이브스\N올려보자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.50,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(745,510)}데킬라\N추가~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,제 친구들도 기대하고 있다고\N아까 로인 보내줬어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 더더욱\N열심히 해야겠네~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그러게요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 맞다!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,내일 라이브\NMC는 어쩔래?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,멤버 소개랑\N곡 소개...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고 뭔가 한 마디씩\N하는 느낌일까요?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!\N괘..괜찮은 거 같아요
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,아니, 지금처럼 하는 것도\N충분하긴 한데 말야~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,히트친 밴드의\N라이브처럼 있지?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,MC로도 재밌게\N분위기 살릴 순 없나 해서~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,재밌는 밴드의\NMC 같은 건 없다
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.60,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,845)\fad(10,10)\fna두리둥실\b1\fs80\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}※ 야마다 개인의 의견입니다
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,팬들이 눈치껏\N좋다고 꺄르륵대는 것뿐이지
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,너무 신랄하잖아!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,820)}인기만 생기면
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,820)}조만간 개똥같은 MC라도\N대폭소를 끌어낼 수 있게 되지
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,820)}안심해!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,820)}음?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,820)}그거\N격려해주는 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,820)}디스하는 거 아냐!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,820)}{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}해산의 위기!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,자!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,싸워서 뭐해요
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,마지막 연습\N열심히 하자구요!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,미안, 미안~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,열심히 해보자!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 간다~?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어라...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}키타 씨, 뭔가...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.44,Default - A,,0,0,0,,아, 괜찮지 않아?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.58,Default - A,,0,0,0,,음!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.34,Default - A,,0,0,0,,다행이네요!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 그래?\N고토 씨...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저기...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브, 조금이라도\N더 달아오르면 좋겠네요
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,응!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,분명 다들\N기대해줄 거라구!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,좋은데!\N긍정적인 자세
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,기대하고 있다구~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,우리 다 함께\N자신감 가져야 하니까요!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,그런 고토 씨를 보고\N모두 깜짝 놀랄지도 모르지!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,아..아니, 그건...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,반드시 그럴 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}왜냐면\N고토 씨는 굉장히―!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,아니~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,아무것도 아냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,열심히 해보자!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,어...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼\N오늘은 여기까지!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,내일 본공연에 대비해서\N각자 빨리 잘 것!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,네~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,수고하셨습니다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,가을 공기네요~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,마음만 같아선 지금 쯤\N미니 앨범 만들 예정이었는데~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,조금씩이라도\N전진하고 있으니 괜찮잖아요
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.33,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna피오피네모\b0\fs70\bord4\c&HD8D7D6&\3c&H3E3C3D&\pos(935,795)}결속밴드
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}마침내...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}문화제 라이브...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}학교 사람들 앞에서\N연주하는...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}첫라이브
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}키타 씨처럼\N"반드시"같은 말은 못하지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}조금이라도...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}모두가 즐겨줬으면\N좋겠어!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,
