Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 언니도 온대~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)}에, 오시는구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(575,980)}자신감을 가져라, 나...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(575,980)}분명 다 좋은 방향으로\N흘러갈 거야...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(575,980)}헛!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(575,980)}어쩌면...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}관객 중에...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,400)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}음반회사 사람이\N있다거나 해서!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,으~마무시하구만~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You들\N바로 데뷔 때리자~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}현역 여고생 밴드의\N성공 스토리...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:41.18,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,10)\fna컴퓨터c\fs60\bord5\c&H2100C7&\3c&H10CCE8&}현역 여고생 밴드\N『결속밴드』 뉴 싱글 6.9 발매
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}뉴스에\N뜨기도 하고...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}전설이 될지도!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,또 혼자만의 세계에\N빠져 있네요~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:56.11,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna말괄량이\fs60\bord6\c&H483531&\3c&HD0CFCD&\pos(970,165)}슈카 축제
