Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:56.11,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna말괄량이\fs25\bord6\c&H483531&\3c&HBBB1AD&\frz4.861\pos(1162.333,826.667)}기대해주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:56.11,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna말괄량이\fs25\bord4\c&H1F1F1F&\3c&H8065B9&\pos(955,410)}체육관 STAGE 타임 스케쥴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩, 가자~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,앞차례 밴드\N반응 좋네~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,이 곡은\N올해 히트쳤으니까요
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)}밴드 라이브에서\N뭔 팬라이트를 흔드냐...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,으앙~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,긴장되기 시작했어!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,키타쨩~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,심호흡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩은~\N괜찮고?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}옙!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}봇치쨩...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}반년 전까지만 해도\N완숙 망고였는데
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}이렇게나 강해 보이는\N표정을 짓게 됐구나!
