Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,결속밴드분들!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,곧 나갈 차례예요!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,네~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,좋았어!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼\N원진이라도 해둘까!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,아!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,손 한 데 모아서\N"오~!" 하는 거 해볼까!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮네요!\N해봐요!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.55,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs50\pos(455,550)}에엑…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,땀내 날 거 같은 짓을...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,다들, 왼손 내밀고!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,네!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,에에에...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,잔말 말고~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨도!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(810,980)}그럼!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(810,980)}열심히 해보자!
