Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,네~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}역시 예상하던\N그대로의 사태가~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,언니~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,힘 내라~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-히토리쨩!
