Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 옭\N좀 바바~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘은 특별히\N컵 술 사 왔지용~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,헤헤헿~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:13.33,Default - A,,0,0,0,,믓찐 연주 때려달라궁~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.31,Default - A,,0,0,0,,웨에이~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:16.39,Default - A,,0,0,0,,웨웨웨에에에~!
